26 Symbols` should float, but the Chrome window (or whatever the parent window was) is not impacted.\n\n## Actual Behavior\n\nThe parent window is being switched into floating mode. Restoring tiling mode via `layout floating tiling` which I have mapped to `alt+s f` fixes the situation. The video below shows the problem in action. I'm placing a terminal window next to Chrome in order to show the impact of the Chrome window going into float mode.\n\nhttps://github.com/nikitabobko/AeroSpace/assets/15000/8e243408-71db-4619-b851-611334fe7d0b\n\nThank you so much for creating this project. Please let me know if this report makes sense or if I can provide more information.","files":null}]}